Multi War Summary

2024-01-22

Summary results over multiple wars

Some notes:
- Respect and Score are slightly different. Respect includes non-war hits, while Score is counting only War hits (i.e.direct contribution to war outcome)
- Chain bonus hits are IGNORED when calculating Net Score (to remove the effects of random bonus hits by low activity members)
- The most useful metric for measuring war performance is probably Net Score. Negative Net Score means the member is costing you points in war, while positive Net Score indicates well-performing members
